data.text:
New York: Alfred A. Knopf, 1950. 1st Edition. Hardcover. Near Fine / Good. Item #012441

8vo. 195pp. Sharp Stated First Edition. Square, tight and clean throughout save some off-setting to gutters. Mild edge-wear. Attractive clipped dust-jacket has some chipping and closed tears. Rubbing to folds. A small pen notation on rear flap. Still bright and complete. A solid collectable copy.
